{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_11_03",
  "title": "奥山すみれ 3話 大きな夢に向かって",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――番組放送当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—On the Day of the Broadcast",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐマラソンのスタート時間だな\n調子はどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The marathon’s starting soon.\nHow are you feeling?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 6.7228797038
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "ばっちりです！　今すぐにでも走り出せます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Perfect! I could start running right now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.7228797038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "頼もしいな。俺も付きっきりとはいかないが\nコースの途中にある休憩所には出来るだけ顔を出すよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s reassuring. I can’t stay with you the whole time‚\nbut I’ll try to stop by the rest areas along the course.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 18.7391156276
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました。特訓した時みたいに\nそばにいて応援してもらえないのは残念ですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Got it. I’ll miss having you right beside me\ncheering me on like during training‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "私には{user}さんに買ってもらった\nキツネのストラップがありますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have the fox charm you bought for me‚\nso I’ll be fine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.4898861964
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "約束通り、これを肌身離さず身に付けて走りますね\n苦しい時はキツネさんを握りしめて頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Just like I promised‚ I’ll keep it with me the whole time.\nWhen it gets tough‚ I’ll hold onto my fox and keep going!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "見ていて下さい！\n絶対に時間内にゴールしてみせますよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please watch me!\nI’ll definitely make it to the goal in time!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.4076397181
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "完走出来るように俺も精一杯サポートするから\nその意気で最後まで頑張れよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ll do everything I can to support you‚\nso keep that spirit and push through to the end.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数時間後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Several Hours Later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.5716970364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8050304253
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8050304253
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……やっと、休憩所に着きました……\nふう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah… hah… I finally made it to the rest area…\nPhew…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.6333318074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。しっかり休んで水分を補給してくれ\n途中で転んだから、痛んだりしたらすぐに言うんだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. Rest well and hydrate properly.\nYou fell earlier—tell me right away if anything hurts.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3999984741,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.4791332324
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫です。道を間違えて、転んじゃって……\n時間をロスして、不安になったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m okay. I took a wrong turn and fell…\nI lost time and got worried‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.2333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.4890223266
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが自転車で駆けつけて\n応援してくれたから、もう平気です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You came rushing over on your bike\nand cheered me on‚ so I’m okay now.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.0333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "体力的に今が一番キツいと思うが、次が最後の休憩所だ\nゴールまでもうひと踏ん張りだぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is probably the toughest point physically‚ but the next stop is the last rest area.\nOne more push and you’ll reach the goal.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.2864999217
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　私には、キツネさんがいますから\nこの子を握りしめて最後まで頑張り……あれ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! I have my fox with me‚\nI’ll hold onto it and keep going to the end—huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.8333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.5118289394
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "ここに付けておいたキツネさんが、なくなってる\nもしかして、途中で落とした？　探しに戻らないと！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The fox I had here… it’s gone.\nDid I drop it somewhere? I have to go back and look!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0333348592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着くんだ\n今戻ったら、それこそ時間内にゴール出来なくなるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down.\nIf you go back now‚ you won’t make it in time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 116.0394450905
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私、走ってて、苦しくて……足が重くて……\n転んで、痛くて……何度も立ち止まりそうになって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But while I was running‚ it was so hard to breathe… my legs felt heavy…\nI fell and got hurt… I almost stopped so many times…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.7000015259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "その度にキツネさんを強く握り締めてきたんです\nそうすれば、{user}さんや……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Every time‚ I squeezed my fox tightly.\nWhen I did that‚ it felt like you‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.1088870766
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr013.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんや、優ちゃんや……応援してくれるみんなが\n背中を押してくれる気がして……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rui-chan‚ Yu-chan… and everyone cheering\nwere pushing me forward…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.9666773479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr014.m4a",
      "text": "そのおかげで、ここまで走って来られたんです\nキツネさんと一緒だったから、私はここまで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s how I made it this far.\nBecause I had my fox with me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.8666773479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.8259625517
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "気持ちは分かるが、瑠依達がゴールで待っているんだ\nすみれはこのマラソンで自分の力を証明するんだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand how you feel‚ but Rui and the others are waiting at the finish line.\nYou’re doing this marathon to prove your own strength‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.046112784,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr015.m4a",
      "text": "……そうですよね。応援してくれている人達のためにも\n今はゴールすることを第一に考えないとダメですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You’re right. For everyone who’s supporting me‚\nI need to focus on reaching the goal first.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.9333440145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.6381388747
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_11_03-smr016.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました……このまま走ります\nごめんね、キツネさん。後でちゃんと探すから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand… I’ll keep running.\nI’m sorry‚ fox. I’ll look for you properly later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.0000106812,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
